238
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,000
Maşallah, maşallah.
 
Mashallah, mashallah.

239
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,000
Wana qaçkê bibînin.
 
Let them see the girls/kids.

240
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,000
Arê, arê, inşallah.
 
Yes, yes, God willing.

241
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,000
Emê han hewşê te, manqê...
 
We are coming to your courtyard, wait...

242
