00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,000
Dore çinar e.
 
Turn of the plane tree.

257
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,000
Asariya.
 
The ruins/fortress.

258
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:11,000
Avo Bahar Xweş, Qanatê Bahar Xweş e.
 
That is Bahar Khwesh, it is the Channel of Bahar Khwesh
