The water comes from the pond/cistern to the man.

289
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,000
Avê şîrketê?
 
City/Company water?

290
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,000
Avê şîrketê?
 
City water?

291
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,000
Sê şem şem tê.
 
It comes every Tuesday.

292
